This table stores information about customer orders placed through the e-commerce store. It tracks the lifecycle of each order, from creation to delivery or return. The table facilitates analysis of order patterns and trends. It also enables understanding of customer behavior related to orders.

This table stores information about users of an e-commerce store. It includes demographic details and geographic locations for each user. The table also tracks the source from which users originated. This data can be used for user segmentation and targeted marketing efforts.
